image:image.image:title: Home - All Are Welcome
image:image.image:caption: Just as the houses in Maywood Park are all different, so are its residents. From young families with children to senior citizens, commuters to telecommuters to retirees, and diversity in religion, race, and gender identity, Maywood Park is a city where all are welcome and included. We stand out as an oasis surrounded by Portland, with easy access to the perks without the hassles of living there.

image:image.image:title: Home - Your City, Your Community
image:image.image:caption: Residents are frequently out walking, or being walked by their dogs. Children play in their yards, on the berm along the Multi-Use Path, and in Maywood Commons. We look out for each other, and youll find a willing helping hand when you need it. Were glad youre here! Welcome to Your City, the City of Maywood Park Oregon! Enjoy, get involved, and LIVE!
